│ sed -i '506,509s/if (II.hasOneUse() && match(Op1, m_Zero()) &&/&\n          │
│ isKnownNonZero(Op0, IC.getSimplifyQuery().getWithInstruction(\&II)) &&/'    │
│ /llvm-autofix-deps/llvm/llvm/llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineCal │
│ ls.cpp                                                                      │
│ ```                                                                         │
